        %h1
          A fair with a festival flair
        %p
          With new, surprisingly designed stands, the fair’s look and layout will bring out the best in the contemporary photography on offer. Unseen has hired renowned industrial and interior design agency Müller van Tol, which made its name with projects for cutting-edge nightspots as well as businesslike environments. For Unseen, Muller van Tol created a floorplan with an open feel. In the impressive hall of the gashouder, with its 60 meter diameter and 14 meter high ceilings, all the galleries are equally prominently present.
        %p
          The clear, open layout is welcoming to visitors. The pavilion at the centre of the construction, 4 meters above the floor, gives visitors access to a panoramic view of all the stands. The latest technology will provide optimal service to visitors and gallerists alike.                        
